<p class="wikiPara">
Hibernate ORM 4.2.0.CR2 was just released. The full changelog can be viewed here: <a href="https://hibernate.onjira.com/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10031&amp;version=12651" target="" class="regularLink">https://hibernate.onjira.com/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10031&amp;version=12651</a>
</p>

<p class="wikiPara">
This is the first release with initial support for OSGi.  Please see <a href="https://hibernate.onjira.com/browse/HHH-7527" target="" class="regularLink">HHH-7527</a> and its subtasks for more information.  Example client bundles can be found here: <a href="https://github.com/brmeyer/HibernateOSGi" target="" class="regularLink">HibernateOSGi</a>
</p>

<p class="wikiPara">
In addition to numerous bug fixes and improvements, this CR was necessary due to a critical regression:
<a href="https://hibernate.onjira.com/browse/HHH-8025" target="" class="regularLink">HHH-8025</a>
</p>

<p class="wikiPara">
As usual, thank you to the community for all the support and hard work!
</p>

